{"type": "article", "id": 22321, "title": "超简洁桌面收纳", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-16T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 154, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133906gmIhby3018KcFlCR.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一套实木做的桌面收纳小件，每一块有 35 厘米长，上面刻出了不同形状的凹槽，一侧是相连的圆孔，另一侧是长方条的凹槽，可以将手机、各类笔插在其中。不同的收纳小件的凹槽有些微的不同，明亮的颜色和文具本身成为桌面的装饰。设计团队 yuue 是创立于德国的中国设计团队，<a href=\"http://www.yuue-design.com/works_zh/one-piece_zh/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133902vrqCNaWZHOEAjluz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133902iEXIVh2G4sgdq7rx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133903sCSt2WFP7er5uwpQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133905MAfV5nINzPutKhb3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}